<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-05-20T16:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-05-20T16:00:00-05:00" n="1063" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1063">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.63/168</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to Special Representative <persName type="to">Rodgers</persName>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-05-20T16:00:00-05:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">May 20, 1916, 4 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>86. Silliman reports Governor Zacatecas decreed all mine owners must
                            begin working within 30 days; otherwise laborers permitted work mines
                            their own account.</p>
                        <p>Take up with appropriate authorities behalf American mine owners,
                            pointing out impossibility their working mines under present disturbed
                            conditions and absence transportation facilities. Endeavor obtain
                            withdrawal decree.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>